Here are some contest guidelines:\n\n\u2022 Contest Dates: 11/1 \u2013 12/6\n\u2022 Where to drop off cans: In the boxes near the tv in the Sport Clubs Office (anytime the Rec is open)\n\u2022 With a sharpie, write your club\u2019s name on the can to indicate it was donated by your club.\n\u2022 There will be a tally sheet on the table.
